en_119501_0	The water levels at Kala oya are increasing rapidly since 12 Sluice gates have been opened at Rajanganaya water reserve today (2) morning.
en_119501_1	Disaster Management Center (DMC) warns the area residents and those who make use of the Kala oya to take precautions due to the prevailing situation.
en_119501_2	The opened sluice gates release 90000 feet water per second to the Kala Oya reports waterways department.
en_119501_3	It further reports that the sluice gates at the Deduru oya reserve and Nachchiduwa are also have been opened today morning.
en_119501_4	(Pix by K. Priyankara)
